updates.title: VAICOM Community Edition for DCS World
updates.releasenotes: Fix Vaicompro.exe not overwriting if running, Adds new option in VaicomPro.exe (Keeper/ Re-launcher App) to run as Administrator, Fix Kneeboard Time zones for Kola & Germany CW, Fix some theaters not showing UHF > VHF > VHF_LOW > HF on kneeboard. Add dual dsiplay of frequencies if avaialble on Kneeboard Pages. Fix module detection routine on some modules SRS settings, Adds MiG-29 Fulcrum reworked, please test
